Package: kdeedu3
Version: 3.0.2
Revision: 2
Depends: kdelibs3-ssl (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdelibs3 (>= 3.0.2-1), kdebase3-ssl (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdebase3 (>= 3.0.2-1), dlcompat, libjpeg-shlibs, libpng-shlibs, qt3-shlibs
BuildDepends: arts-dev (>= 1.0.2-1), kdelibs3-ssl-dev (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdelibs3-dev (>= 3.0.2-1), kdebase3-ssl-dev (>= 3.0.2-1) | kdebase3-dev (>= 3.0.2-1), automake15, autoconf25, libtool14, fink (>= 0.9.12), dlcompat, libjpeg, libpng, qt3
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Source: http://download.kde.org/stable/%v/src/kdeedu-%v.tar.bz2
Source-MD5: 0c7950ada06e11ac4e62c7105aeca32c
PatchScript: sed 's|@PREFIX@|%p|g' <%a/%f.patch | patch -p0
SetLDFLAGS: -L%p/lib
SetCPPFLAGS: -no-cpp-precomp
SetCFLAGS: -fno-common
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p --with-qt-dir=%p --with-extra-libs=%p/lib --with-extra-includes=%p/include --enable-mt --with-pic --enable-rpath --enable-shared=yes --enable-static=yes --mandir=%i/share/man --with-xinerama --enable-final $KDEOPTS
CompileScript: <<
 make -f Makefile.cvs
 (export KDEDIR=%p; sh configure %c; make)
<<
InstallScript: <<
 make install DESTDIR=%d
<<
DocFiles: COPYING INSTALL README
Description: KDE - educational software
DescDetail: <<
  Educational software for KDE.
<<
DescPort: <<
Nothing special needed other than the admin/ patch from kdebase.

NOTE: KDE packages do *not* have an -shlibs because of KDE's use of  
libltdl!  The .la's *must* be used in conjunction with the dynamic
libraries, and they are unversioned filenames, so multiple -shlibs would
conflict.
<<
